.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-FEE-PROPORTIONAL-MIN" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-fee-proportional-min \- FEAT-2782 channel-fee-proportional-min
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-fee-proportional-min
.SH DESCRIPTION
Reports the minimum fee_proportional_millionths across all peer channels (FEAT-2782).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN with key \fBfee_proportional_min\fR.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
